Invocation Name: seventies quiz
des:
70s Quiz is part of Wayback Quiz.

70s Quiz will test your knowledge of nineteen seventies pop culture, sport and headlines.

You will get 10 questions on different topics... every answer is True or False!

Can you remember who directed Smokey and the Bandit? Or which TV channel Blake's 7 was on?

Relive your youth, maybe remember some long forgotten great books, films, video games and TV... and some terrible number one singles you'd rather forget.

Play on your own or with friends - who can get the highest score?

70s Quiz is part of Wayback Quiz. If you launch this skill, it will ask for permission to open Wayback Quiz.
priv: The developer reported that this skill does not collect personal information.
